ado-com-covid-19-em-portugal-11936785.html?fbclid=IwAR2o7D1th7V1VA3XDc6wpmuIhpt13VkNg2U8sH6bnWNml57U66MD2VVuUIg|title=Morreu um infetado com Covid-19 em Portugal|date=16 March 2020|work=Jornal de Noticias|access-date=|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{URL |1=https://www.dgs.pt/em-destaque/relatorio-de-situacao-n-015-17032020-pdf.aspx |2=2020-03-17 }}\n|58\n|38\n|20\n|0\n|1\n|0\n|0\n|1\n|117\n|448\n|\n|\n|0\n|1\n|0\n|3\n|\n|-\n|{{URL |1=https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/i026029.pdf |2=2020-03-18 }}\n|93\n|63\n|23\n|2\n|7\n|1\n|2\n|3\n|194\n|642\n|\n|\n|1\n|2\n|0\n|3\n|<ref name=\"lifestyle.sapo.pt\">{{Cite web|url=https://lifestyle.sapo.pt/saude/noticias-saude/artigos/vieira-monteiro-e-a-segunda-vitima-mortal-por-covid-19-em-portugal|title=Presidente do Santander, Vieira Monteiro, \u00e9 a segunda v\u00edtima mortal por COVID-19 em Portugal|last=|first=|date=18 March 2020|website=lifestyle.sapo.pt|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=18 March 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"anmsp200319\">{{cite web|url=https://www.anmsp.pt/covid19|title=Casos confirmados de COVID-19 em Portugal|author=Associa\u00e7\u00e3o Nacional de M\u00e9dicos de Sa\u00fade P\u00fablica|date=2020-03-18|access-date=2020-03-18}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{URL |1=https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/17_DGS_boletim_20200319.pdf.pdf |2=2020-03-19 }}\n|92\n|35\n|12\n|0\n|4\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|143\n|785\n|\n|\n|1\n|3\n|0\n|3\n|\n|-\n|{{URL |1=https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/18_DGS_boletim_20200320-1.pdf |2=2020-03-20 }}\n|125\n|83\n|20\n|0\n|4\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|235\n|1020\n|126\n|26\n|3\n|6\n|2\n|5\n|\n|-\n|{{URL |1=https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/19_DGS_boletim_20200321.pdf |2=2020-03-21 }}\n|138\n|87\n|31\n|1\n|2\n|4\n|0\n|0\n|260\n|1280\n|156\n|35\n|6\n|12\n|0\n|5\n|\n|-\n|{{URL |1=https://covid19.min-saude.pt/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/i026051.pdf |2=2020-03-22 }}\n|181\n|86\n|43\n|2\n|4\n|2\n|1\n|1\n|320\n|1600\n|169\n|41\n|2\