te)|George Davidson]], S Crewther, Cargill, [[Nelson Bass]] 2, [[Lou Brown (rugby league)|Lou Brown]] 3, Mackay\n| con1 = [[George Davidson (rugby league)|George Davidson]], S Crewther 3\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = Seagar, McGregor\n| con2 = Seagar\n| pen2 = Seagar\n| stadium = Carlaw Park 2\n| attendance =\n| referee = Saunders\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 9 August\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Devonport\n| score = 21-6\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =League Championship/Club Matches Resumed\n| page =3\n| publisher =New Zealand Herald, Volume LXI, Issue 18784\n| date = 1924-08-11\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19240811.2.6\n| accessdate = 2019-09-09}}</ref>\n| away = Ellerslie\n| try1 = A Harper 3, L Voysey, [[Stan Webb (rugby league)|Stan Webb]]\n| con1 = Scott 3\n| pen1 =\n| try2 =\n| con2 =\n| pen2 = Peebles, Shand 2\n| stadium = Victoria Park 1\n| attendance =\n| referee = H C Taylor\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 9 August\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Newton\n| score = 12-11\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =League Championship/Club Matches Resumed\n| page =3\n| publisher =New Zealand Herald, Volume LXI, Issue 18784\n| date = 1924-08-11\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19240811.2.6\n| accessdate = 2019-09-09}}</ref>\n| away = Mangere\n| try1 = Moran, Jack Keenan\n| con1 = Mansell\n| pen1 = Mansell 2\n| try2 = T Pai, Wilson jr., [[Jim Rukutai]]\n| con2 = T Pai\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Victoria Park 2\n| attendance =\n| referee = R McCowatt\n}}\n \n===Round 12===\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 16 August\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Ponsonby\n| score = 25-10\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Ponsonby Defeat City\n| page = 4\n| publisher = New Zealand Herald, Volume LXI, Issue 18790\n| date = 1924-08-18\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19240818.2.11.1\n| accessdate = 2019-09-09}}</ref>\n| away = City\n| try1 = Mormon, [[Ivan Littlewood]] 2, Donovan, Peckham\n| con1 = [[Frank D