September 25, 2018}}</ref>\n| ''Lauren''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| 2013\n|[[Streamy Awards|Streamy Award]]\n| Best Female Performance \u2013 Drama<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.streamys.org/nominees-winners/3rd-annual-nominees/|title=3rd Annual Winners & Nominees {{!}} The Streamy Awards|work=The Streamy Awards|access-date=September 25, 2018|language=en-US}}</ref>\n| ''Lauren''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2013\n| [[2013 Teen Choice Awards|Teen Choice Awards]]\n|[[Teen Choice Award for Choice TV Actress Drama|Choice TV Actress: Drama]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1712166/teen-choice-awards-2013-winners/|title=2013 Teen Choice Awards: The Winners List|work=MTV News|access-date=September 25, 2018|language=en}}</ref>\n| ''Pretty Little Liars''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| 2014\n| IAWTV Award\n| Best Female Performance \u2013 Drama<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.iawtv.org/iawtv-awards-ap/|title=IAWTV Awards - Past Winners|website=International Academy of Web Television|language=en-US|access-date=September 25, 2018}}</ref>\n| ''[[WIGS (YouTube channel)|Lauren]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{IMDb name|0069079}}\n* {{Twitter}}\n\n{{Teen Choice Award Choice TV Actress Drama|state=collapsed}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bellisario, Troian}}\n[[Category:1985 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:20th-century American actresses]]\n[[Category:21st-century American actresses]]\n[[Category:Actresses from Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:American child actresses]]\n[[Category:American film actresses]]\n[[Category:American people of Italian descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Serbian descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Creole descent]]\n[[Category:American television actresses]]\n[[Category:USC School of Dramatic Arts alumni]]\n[[Category:Actresses of Italian descent]]\n[[Category:Actresses of Serbian descent]]\n[[Category:Bellisario family]]\n", "name_user": "Davey2010", "label": "safe", "comment"